sources.title: Steel Frontier - Full Movie
sources.description:
“Mad Max” meets “Man with No Name” in this futuristic story of a gunfighter who goes after a band of marauders that is terrorizing and killing indiscriminately. As with spaghetti westerns, the lone gunman enters a town where the people have lost the will to fight back and he proceeds to kill off the bad guys single-handedly. But once he is wounded, a few do find the will to rise up.
